  <summary>3/3/1988--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to terminate, as of January 1, 1989, the permitted exclusion from the taxable gross income of U.S. citizens and residents working abroad of: (1) foreign earned income; and (2) eligible housing expenses.</summary>
